<plot>Blake Poopler follows the surreal experience of a depressed New England bartender as he moves from his longtime home in Boston to the paranoid confines of Brooklyn, New York. A Florida vacation triggers Blake's decision to leave the restaurant job and lifestyle that he has grown tired of. Blake relocates to Greenpoint, Brooklyn, but is unable to find true happiness. His friends and addictions come back to haunt him as he takes a turn towards introspective madness after swallowing a tab of acid. This movie is an experimental hyperreal docu-drama with moments of surreal comedy and drug-related confusion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?074129</url></doc>
